%% WS 断线重连 + /api/sync 补齐全流程 —— 最终兜底
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Client
    participant G as gateway pod (可能与之前不同)
    participant R as Redis routing
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over C,G: 场景：客户端网络抖动 / 后台挂起，WS 断开 T 秒

    C-xG: WS 断开 (TCP FIN / 超时)
    G->>G: readPump 退出<br/>conn.Close()<br/>hub.Deregister(conn)<br/>routing.Deregister(uid, deviceID)
    Note over R: HDEL im-new:routing:user:{uid} {deviceID}<br/>若为最后一个 device，HASH 自动变空 key

    Note over C: T 秒后客户端重连<br/>本地仍持有 {chID → seq} 游标

    C->>G: GET /ws?token=...&device=...
    G->>G: JWT 校验 → NewConn → hub.Register<br/>routing.Register(uid, deviceID) ← Redis 重新写入 pod 身份
    G->>C: WS Upgrade 成功<br/>（conn.knownSeq = {} 刚建，服务端还不知道客户端已经有哪些 seq）

    Note over C,G: 客户端必须立即做两件事之一：<br/>① 发 WS {type:"sync", channels:[...]} 建立基准<br/>② 调 POST /api/sync 同时建基准 + 拉消息
    C->>G: POST /api/sync<br/>{channels:[{id:42,seq:130}, {id:88,seq:5}, {id:99,seq:180}]}

    G->>DB: GetMemberChannelSeqs(uid)
    DB-->>G: {42:130, 88:5, 99:200, 777:12}  ← 服务端真相

    loop 对每个 serverSeq
        alt client_seq >= server_seq
            G->>G: 跳过 (chID 42, 88 已对齐)
        else 新频道 (客户端没提交过)
            G->>DB: FetchForUser(chID, uid, afterSeq=serverSeq-50, limit=50)
            DB-->>G: 最近 50 条
            G->>G: delta.has_more = (serverSeq > 50)
            Note over G: chID 777 新加入 → 返最近 50 + has_more
        else gap <= 100 (SyncGapThreshold)
            G->>DB: FetchForUser(chID, uid, afterSeq=clientSeq, limit=100)
            DB-->>G: 补全的 messages
            Note over G: chID 99: gap=20 → 直接返 181..200
        else gap > 100
            G->>DB: FetchForUser(chID, uid, afterSeq=serverSeq-50, limit=50)
            G->>G: delta.has_more = true
            Note over G: 大缺口 fast-forward：只给最近 50<br/>客户端要翻更旧要 GET /messages?before_seq=
        end
        G->>G: 计算 unread = (srvSeq - last_read_seq) - (phantom_count - phantom_at_read)
    end

    G-->>C: {channels:[{id,server_seq,unread,messages,has_more}, ...]}
    C->>C: 落库 + 更新本地 {chID → seq}<br/>后续 ping 携带最新 seq → pong diff 归零
